# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Dr. Rahul Tengse Website — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. Copy this file to .env in the project root
#   2. Fill in confirmed values before deploying
#   3. For Netlify: add these in Site Settings → Environment Variables
#   4. .env is gitignored — never commit it
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── REQUIRED FOR PRODUCTION ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

# VITE_SITE_URL — the live domain for the website (no trailing slash)
# Used by: SEO utility (canonical URLs, OG image absolute URL),
#          sitemap.xml and robots.txt (replaced by scripts/prepare-assets.mjs postbuild)
# Example: VITE_SITE_URL=https://drrahultengse.com
VITE_SITE_URL=

# ── REQUIRED FOR WHATSAPP APPOINTMENT FLOW ───────────────────────────────────

# VITE_WHATSAPP_NUMBER — confirmed 10-digit Indian WhatsApp number (no +91 prefix)
# Client must confirm whether this is the doctor's personal number or hospital
# reception number before setting this value.
# Example: VITE_WHATSAPP_NUMBER=9876543210
# Leave empty to disable WhatsApp redirect (Call Now fallback will be shown).
VITE_WHATSAPP_NUMBER=

# ── FUTURE: BACKEND API (v2) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

# VITE_API_BASE_URL — base URL of the backend API (leave blank for v1 frontend-only)
# When backend is ready, set this and activate the api.js utility.
# Example: VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.drrahultengse.com
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
